## Architecture: Data Pipeline

```
Video/Audio File
      ↓
faster-whisper (transcription)
      ↓
Google Translate API (Hindi → English)
      ↓
LLM Flagging (GPT-4) — flags unclear segments, does NOT alter
      ↓
[Quality Gate] confidence threshold check
      ↓
Semantic Chunking — sliding window with overlap (~paragraph sized)
      ↓
Metadata Tagging (GPT-4) — topics, trust score, source, session ID
      ↓
Embedding (text-embedding-3-small)
      ↓
[Quality Gate] semantic consistency vs AP Framework
      ↓
Qdrant Vector DB (local)
```

## Architecture: Query Pipeline

```
User Query (CLI)
      ↓
Translation Layer — maps user vocab → philosopher vocab
      (AP Framework in system prompt)
      (Intent classification: high confidence → translate,
       low confidence → suggest related queries,
       no match → redirect with query suggestions)
      ↓
Search Orchestrator
      → Qdrant: semantic similarity search
      → Rank by: trust score + semantic relevance + explanation clarity
      → Assemble context window (lost-in-middle aware ordering)
         - Beginning: AP Framework excerpts, highest trust chunks
         - Middle: lower trust / supplementary content
         - End: reviewed transcripts, concrete examples
      ↓
LLM Generation (GPT-4)
      (system prompt: AP Framework + concept glossary + faithfulness instructions)
      ↓
CLI Output
```

